snippet.title: American Amber/Red Ale Review. (All grain addition)
snippet.description:
Hi all thank you for taking the time to watching this video. today I review my American Amber ale and compare it with The Abernethy Brothers Brewery's original brew. It is a very nice brew.   Please enjoy. 

Abernethy Brothers Brewery:  https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQ5apdWDUyiz_OWvMo2DgMA/featured
